my Princess Jade fell.

277
00:13:03,850 --> 00:13:05,930
I saw my Dream Tapir Demon form.

278
00:13:09,590 --> 00:13:10,790
19 years ago,

279
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:14,610
Qionghua waged war with the Dream Tapir Demon Clan.

280
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,680
My parents in Shouyang...

281
00:13:17,490 --> 00:13:18,550
Their biological daughter

282
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:20,680
