283
00:13:22,110 --> 00:13:25,030
Uncle Ziying's master, too.

284
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:27,630
It's destined.

285
00:13:28,810 --> 00:13:30,600
I can't stay with you anymore.

286
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:38,580
But you're still Qionghua's disciple.

287
00:13:38,970 --> 00:13:41,760
You even helped Sect Leader Xu Liang resolve his problem.

288
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:45,890
You even went to find the cold weapon to help Senior Xuan Xiao break the ice.

289
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,480
You've done so many good deeds.

290
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,950
I don't care if you're a human or a demon.

291
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,030
You are my good Mengli.

292
00:13:58,750 --> 00:13:59,550
Lingsha.

293
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:03,470
Now you know I'm a demon,

294
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:06,590
