297
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:13,960
Qionghua used to kill demons.

298
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:16,260
But you won't be evil.

299
00:14:16,570 --> 00:14:18,630
You are Tianhe and my family forever.

300
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:21,580
Mengli.

301
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:27,490
If you don't want to go back to Qionghua,

302
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:29,630
wait for Lingsha and me to send the Kun Scale back.

303
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:31,430
After we help Brother Xuan Xiao break the ice,

304
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:34,230
we'll come back to Qingluan Peak to accompany you.

305
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:36,180
As long as our kinship remains the same,

306
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,580
no matter how you change,

307
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,020
we won't change.

308
00:14:41,830 --> 00:14:42,760
Thank you.

309
00:14:47,950 --> 00:14:48,790
Cheer up.

310
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:12,290
Mengli.

311
00:15:12,830 --> 00:15:15,070
Are you really not going back to Qionghua with us?

312
00:15:15,070 --> 00:15:17,400
The three of us haven't separated before.

313
00:15:18,150 --> 00:15:19,260
If I go back,

314
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:22,290
I'm afraid I can't hide my identity for long.

315
00:15:22,290 --> 00:15:23,490
You can go back first.

316
00:15:23,950 --> 00:15:25,410
I will take care of myself.

317
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:26,710
Qingluan Peak

318
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:28,870
was the second home Uncle Yun left me.

319
00:15:39,950 --> 00:15:42,280
Those self-righteous cultivating sects

320
00:15:42,340 --> 00:15:44,750
will never leave a place for demons.

321
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,380
Wake up, Young Master.

322
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:48,940
Guixie, what are you doing here?

323
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,090
Since you know your origin,

324
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:53,200
I don't have to hide it anymore.

325
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,470
I'm Guixie, the demon general of Huanming Realm.

326
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:56,600
According to seniority,

327
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:58,240
you should call me uncle.

328
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,030
Nonsense!

329
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,570
How could Mengli be like you?

330
00:16:02,110 --> 00:16:04,510
You're the evil demon who killed the Elder Zong Lian.

331
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,350
That old man was the culprit

332
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:07,110
