333
00:16:07,490 --> 00:16:08,490
It's not just him.

334
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:10,200
Everyone from the Qionghua Sect deserves to die.

335
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:12,500
You didn't come all the way to Qingluan Peak

336
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,360
