341
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,030
You really do have the Kun Scale.

342
00:16:36,580 --> 00:16:37,110
No!

343
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:46,040
Do you think I should kill you first

344
00:16:46,570 --> 00:16:48,920
or destroy it first?

345
00:16:48,970 --> 00:16:49,900
I'll go with you.

346
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:51,660
Let go of Lingsha and Tianhe.

347
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:52,820
Don't destroy the Kun Scale.

348
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:54,950
What I want to destroy is the Kun Scale.

349
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:57,070
Without this third cold weapon,

350
00:16:57,070 --> 00:16:58,530
how can you save Xuan Xiao?

351
00:16:58,950 --> 00:17:00,230
How will the Qionghua Sect dare

352
00:17:00,230 --> 00:17:02,890
to compete with the Huanming Realm without him?

353
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:22,890
Tianhe!

354
00:17:25,910 --> 00:17:28,349
I can't let you destroy the Kun Scale.

355
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:32,120
I want to protect Brother Xuan Xiao.

356
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:35,010
Let's see how a dead person can save others.

357
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:45,640
You're a Dream Tapir Demon. How can you protect a human?

358
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,290
He is the most important person to me.

359
00:17:47,290 --> 00:17:48,750
He has been protecting me.

360
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,470
Xi Zhong, what are you doing?

361
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,550
Mengli! Tianhe!

362
00:17:58,250 --> 00:17:58,960
Xi Zhong.

363
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:00,950
How dare you ruin my plan!

364
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,300
Where did they go?

365
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,200
Uncle Ziying.

366
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,440
Uncle Ziying!

367
00:18:21,370 --> 00:18:22,770
Tianhe, are you alright?

368
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,080
I'm fine.

369
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:25,940
Why are we at Boxian Town?

370
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:27,480
Where is Lingsha?

371
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:30,320
Don't worry.

372
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:32,440
That girl is out of danger.

373
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,480
You are indeed Luo.

374
00:18:36,940 --> 00:18:38,240
I'm your mother's guard.

375
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,300
My name is Xi Zhong.

376
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:40,460
My mother?

377
00:18:40,730 --> 00:18:42,540
Your mother is Chan You.

378
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:44,510
She named you Yuan Luo.

379
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:46,640
For the past 19 years,

380
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:48,820
she has been missing you all the time.

381
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:50,970
She must be so happy to see you.

382
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:53,110
Let's go home

383
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,170
and reunite with your mother.

384
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:00,390
Mengli.

385
00:19:01,620 --> 00:19:02,580
I think

386
00:19:02,910 --> 00:19:04,570
he doesn't look like a bad guy.

387
00:19:05,090 --> 00:19:06,490
Since he came to save you,

388
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:08,540
he likely wouldn't lie to you.

389
00:19:11,020 --> 00:19:11,660
Mengli,

390
00:19:12,150 --> 00:19:13,750
didn't you go through so much

391
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:15,310
just to find your mother?

392
00:19:17,470 --> 00:19:18,590
If you are afraid,

393
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:20,670
Lingsha and I will go with you.

394
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,910
As humans, aren't you afraid

395
00:19:23,230 --> 00:19:25,030
of entering the Huanming Realm?

396
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:26,230
I swore

397
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,670
to protect Mengli and Lingsha for the rest of my life.

398
00:19:28,670 --> 00:19:29,870
Kid, you should know.

399
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:32,030
The human race's lifespan

400
00:19:32,450 --> 00:19:33,710
is just a moment for us.

401
00:19:34,190 --> 00:19:35,720
That's none of my business.

402
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:36,720
I only know that

403
00:19:36,890 --> 00:19:38,820
family should protect each other.

404
00:19:38,940 --> 00:19:40,940
I'll protect her for as long as I can.

405
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:43,310
I've been trying to find out who I am.

406
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:45,750
But I'm not Yuan Luo of Huanming Realm.

407
00:19:45,750 --> 00:19:47,810
I am Liu Mengli from the mortal world.

408
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:49,710
My home and my family are here.

409
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,350
I won't go with you.

410
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:52,140
But...

411
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,440
Why do you still force her?

412
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:58,910
Although she has the blood of the Dream Tapir Demon Clan,

413
00:19:58,910 --> 00:20:01,770
