414
00:20:01,810 --> 00:20:02,570
Do you know?

415
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:04,820
The young master you've been looking for...

416
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:07,080
She wants to help Xuan Xiao break the ice.

417
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:09,390
You want to help Xuan Xiao break the ice?

418
00:20:09,390 --> 00:20:11,250
The third cold weapon, Kun Scale,

419
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,490
is with that brat.

420
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:19,650
Should I tell Feng Er

421
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,320
or Su Yao?

422
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,910
Tianhe really found the Kun Scale?

423
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:26,390
Yes.

424
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:29,530
Tianhe said it himself. He wouldn't lie about it.

425
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,120
With three cold weapons,

426
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:33,970
Xuan Xiao can break the ice immediately.

427
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:35,630
Heaven is on our side.

428
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,780
When will they come back?

429
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:40,490
They should have returned to Qionghua by now.

430
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:41,490
I'm guessing that

431
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:43,470
Tianhe hadn't returned to Qingluan Peak for a long time.

432
00:20:43,470 --> 00:20:45,080
So he's spending more time there.

433
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:45,880
Grandmaster,

434
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:48,580
where is Master Su Shen now?

435
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,110
Uncle Ziying!

436
00:20:53,930 --> 00:20:54,540
Go away!

437
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:56,460
Uncle Ziying,

438
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:58,090
please save Tianhe and Mengli.

439
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:58,950
What happened?

440
00:20:59,330 --> 00:21:01,070
When we were leaving Qingluan Peak,

441
00:21:01,070 --> 00:21:02,310
we were stopped by the

442
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,350
Dream Tapir Demon named Guixie.

443
00:21:03,350 --> 00:21:04,230
Guixie again?

444
00:21:04,430 --> 00:21:06,490
Did they try to destroy the Kun Scale?

445
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:07,910
At the most critical moment,

446
00:21:07,910 --> 00:21:09,110
a big light hole appeared behind

447
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:10,270
Tianhe and Mengli.

448
00:21:10,670 --> 00:21:12,260
A Dream Tapir Demon stood in that hole.

449
00:21:12,260 --> 00:21:14,120
They took Tianhe and Mengli away.

450
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:16,070
Then Guixie went after them too.

451
00:21:17,830 --> 00:21:18,630
Uncle Ziying,

452
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,050
use your spiritual power to find out

453
00:21:20,050 --> 00:21:21,610
where they sent Tianhe and Mengli to.

454
00:21:21,610 --> 00:21:21,940
Okay.

455
00:21:28,410 --> 00:21:30,740
The Dream Tapir Demon Clan has appeared in Boxian Town.

456
00:21:30,740 --> 00:21:32,340
Come quickly to subdue them.

457
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,960
Let's follow the demonic aura.

458
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:37,240
Wait.

459
00:21:41,150 --> 00:21:43,230
I received a talisman message from Boxian Town.

460
00:21:43,230 --> 00:21:44,910
A Dream Tapir Demon was sighted there.

461
00:21:44,910 --> 00:21:46,040
It should be Guixie.

462
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:48,830
Guixie is the general of the Dream Tapir Demons.

463
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:49,630
Grandmaster,

464
00:21:49,630 --> 00:21:51,000
I'm afraid we have to go together

465
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:53,550
