466
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:55,410
We're not going to kill the demon.

467
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:57,120
We must protect the Kun Scale,

468
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,800
Tianhe, and Mengli.

469
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:00,180
Su Xi,

470
00:22:00,640 --> 00:22:02,370
you, Ziying, and Sect Leader Xu Yi

471
00:22:02,370 --> 00:22:04,170
shall lead the disciples there.

472
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:04,750
Yes.

473
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:05,420
Yes.

474
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:07,570
Let's go.

475
00:22:16,340 --> 00:22:17,380
Tianhe, Mengli!

476
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,030
Lingsha.

477
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:19,240
Lingsha.

478
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:22,350
What?

479
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:24,490
Is Su Yao too scared to meet me?

480
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:25,540
We're enough

481
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:26,990
to deal with you.

482
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,140
Guixie must die.

483
00:22:29,840 --> 00:22:33,100
Today, I'll let you pay with your life for Master Zong Lian.

484
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,770
You're Zong Lian's disciple?

485
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:36,940
Did you receive his broken sword?

486
00:22:37,210 --> 00:22:38,200
Do you like it?

487
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:39,560
Ziying,

488
00:22:39,970 --> 00:22:41,830
remember what Grandmaster said.

489
00:22:44,910 --> 00:22:46,110
Set up the formation!

490
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:47,670
Ziying,

491
00:22:47,950 --> 00:22:49,650
can you not use the Demon Slaying Formation?

492
00:22:49,650 --> 00:22:50,380
Don't worry.

493
00:22:50,710 --> 00:22:54,170
The Demon Slaying Formation only targets demons, not humans.

494
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:04,910
Mengli!

495
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:15,990
Mengli!

496
00:23:22,980 --> 00:23:23,710
Stop!

497
00:23:24,220 --> 00:23:25,820
If you don't stop the formation,

498
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:26,970
