499
00:23:26,970 --> 00:23:28,700
Yun Tianhe, what are you doing?

500
00:23:29,090 --> 00:23:29,810
Move!

501
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:31,500
Tianhe.

502
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:34,230
Ziying, Grandmaster said

503
00:23:34,550 --> 00:23:36,880
we just need to protect Tianhe and Mengli.

504
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:41,710
Ziying.

505
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:48,980
End the formation!

506
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:00,660
Come with me.

507
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:02,970
Mengli!

508
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,070
Yun Tianhe,

509
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:07,920
As a Qionghua disciple,

510
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:09,740
you sided with the Dream Tapir Demon Clan.

511
00:24:09,740 --> 00:24:11,090
What should your punishment be?

512
00:24:11,090 --> 00:24:12,550
Then, I won't be a disciple

513
00:24:13,430 --> 00:24:14,630
of Qionghua anymore.

514
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:16,230
Yun Tianhe,

515
00:24:17,150 --> 00:24:18,280
you gave up Qionghua

516
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:20,310
for demons?

517
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:21,510
Why?

518
00:24:22,710 --> 00:24:23,380
Ziying,

519
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,580
