524
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:35,650
Nephew Ziying.

525
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:37,980
Yun Tianhe is your disciple.

526
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:39,720
I'll leave it to you.

527
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,240
Let's go.

528
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:48,670
Yun Tianhe.

529
00:24:49,610 --> 00:24:51,810
