534
00:24:58,470 --> 00:24:59,530
I'm sorry, Ziying.

535
00:25:01,150 --> 00:25:03,610
I just want to save as many lives as possible.

536
00:25:04,010 --> 00:25:04,700
Fine.

537
00:25:05,710 --> 00:25:06,310
Today,

538
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,450
