543
00:25:17,690 --> 00:25:20,090
I will protect the demons I should protect.

544
00:25:27,510 --> 00:25:28,190
Fine.

545
00:25:29,850 --> 00:25:31,290
That's the difference

546
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:33,870
in the Way of our hearts.

547
00:26:00,690 --> 00:26:02,890
Today, we will cut off our brotherhood.

548
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:04,670
From now on,

549
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:06,750
you are no longer

550
00:26:07,660 --> 00:26:08,630
related to me

551
00:26:10,070 --> 00:26:11,550
or Qionghua.

552
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:41,640
I'll tell Uncle Ziying that

553
00:26:41,690 --> 00:26:43,500
the demon you want to protect is me.

554
00:26:43,500 --> 00:26:44,140
Mengli.

555
00:26:45,670 --> 00:26:46,430
It's okay.

556
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:47,750
I believe Ziying.

557
00:26:48,390 --> 00:26:49,990
He will understand someday.

558
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:53,960
Mengli, Lingsha,

559
00:26:54,110 --> 00:26:55,970
wait for me at Qingfeng Pavilion.

560
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,640
I'll go to Qionghua and give the Kun Scale to Brother Xuan Xiao.

561
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,440
I'll go too.

562
00:27:00,540 --> 00:27:02,670
Consider it the last time I see Ziying.

563
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:14,440
Grandmaster,

564
00:27:15,020 --> 00:27:18,020
Yun Tianhe and Han Lingsha have returned to Qionghua.

565
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:25,720
After all, the three of them

566
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:28,740
have contributed to finding the cold weapons.

567
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:32,830
Let him send the Kun Scale to the forbidden area first.

568
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:34,870
If he decides to leave,

569
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:37,280
I won't give him a hard time.

570
00:27:37,820 --> 00:27:38,510
Yes.

571
00:27:42,460 --> 00:27:42,980
Ziying.

572
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:46,440
Yun Tianhe can leave.

573
00:27:46,900 --> 00:27:48,960
But the Wangshu Sword must stay here.

574
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:51,910
Wangshu Sword

575
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:55,220
is crucial to the attack against the Huanming Demon Clan.

576
00:27:55,220 --> 00:27:56,070
You must

577
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:59,350
bring Wangshu back from Yun Tianhe.

578
00:28:00,060 --> 00:28:00,790
Understood.

579
00:28:05,270 --> 00:28:06,070
Grandmaster,

580
00:28:06,570 --> 00:28:08,700
Master Su Shen promised to wait for me.

581
00:28:08,990 --> 00:28:10,390
Is she still in Qionghua?

582
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:12,310
She...

583
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,510
Where is she?

584
00:28:20,710 --> 00:28:21,690
She's...

585
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:28,050
She is...

586
00:28:30,490 --> 00:28:31,950
in the Thousand-Man Tomb.

587
00:28:50,170 --> 00:28:52,230
[Qingfeng Pavilion]

588
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:01,980
Young Master.

589
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:03,830
Young Master.

590
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:05,570
Young Master, is that you?

591
00:29:06,190 --> 00:29:07,590
Are you in this painting?

592
00:29:13,110 --> 00:29:14,950
Could this Princess Jade

593
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:17,430
be hindering my connection with him?

594
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,590
Greetings, Young Master, I'm Jing Chen.

595
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:34,370
Why do you all call me Young Master?

596
00:29:34,370 --> 00:29:36,370
Because your mother, Lord Chan You,

597
00:29:36,630 --> 00:29:39,030
is the Dream Tapir Demon Chief of the Huanming Realm.

598
00:29:39,030 --> 00:29:40,160
Since you were born,

599
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:42,010
I've been your personal guard.

600
00:29:46,150 --> 00:29:49,400
My birth mother is the demon chief?

601
00:29:50,390 --> 00:29:52,610
According to the Qionghua History Book,

602
00:29:52,610 --> 00:29:56,740
it was the demon chief who led the demons to wreak havoc in the mortal world.

603
00:29:57,340 --> 00:29:58,670
Qionghua is framing us.

604
00:29:59,080 --> 00:29:59,880
Young Master.

605
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:02,560
Back then, Qionghua attacked us first.

606
00:30:02,810 --> 00:30:05,160
We Dream Tapir Demon Clan only wanted to protect ourselves.

607
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:07,020
Back then, Shouyang was in chaos.

608
00:30:07,630 --> 00:30:09,520
My foster parents' biological daughter

609
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:11,580
was killed by the Dream Tapir Demons.

610
00:30:11,670 --> 00:30:13,910
They were behind all the matters after that.

611
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:15,070
I witnessed it myself.

612
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:15,870
No.

613
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:23,310
What's wrong?

614
00:30:23,390 --> 00:30:25,470
I only have my primordial spirit.

615
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:28,250
I can't stay outside for too long.

616
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:29,990
If you want to know the truth,

617
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:33,430
you can summon the two generals, Guixie and Xi Zhong.

618
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:35,090
Huanming is innocent.

619
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:51,070
Everyone has emotions and desires.

620
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:54,000
Therefore, disputes are inevitable.

621
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:56,350
As long as there is a chance to meet,

622
00:30:57,210 --> 00:30:59,210
there will be room for reconciling.

623
00:31:00,390 --> 00:31:02,790
The worst thing is to say goodbye in silence

624
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:04,520
and never see each other again

625
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:07,390
even in death.

626
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:10,440
Even if you want to be forgiven,

627
00:31:11,660 --> 00:31:13,460
you won't have a chance anymore.

628
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:15,710
Are you

629
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:17,490
talking about my parents?

630
00:31:20,950 --> 00:31:21,640
Tianhe,

631
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,510
don't be upset.

632
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:27,230
Everyone in this world will leave you.

633
00:31:27,430 --> 00:31:28,470
But your heart

634
00:31:30,070 --> 00:31:31,900
will follow you forever.

635
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:35,110
Maintaining what you think

636
00:31:35,990 --> 00:31:37,250
is the most important.

637
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:40,520
If Murong Ziying understands you,

638
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:42,240
he will come back to you.

639
00:31:43,420 --> 00:31:45,080
If he doesn't understand you,

640
00:31:45,330 --> 00:31:46,490
just leave him.

641
00:31:48,460 --> 00:31:49,460
I understand now.

642
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:53,270
I will maintain what I think.

643
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,310
Tianhe,

644
00:32:16,350 --> 00:32:19,270
I've gathered the spiritual power of the three cold weapons.

645
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:21,800
My spiritual cultivation is even higher now.

646
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:23,920
You should leave first.

647
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:27,110
I will use my power to break the ice later.

648
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:29,160
It will surely affect the surroundings.

649
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,690
I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

650
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:37,330
Brother.

651
00:32:39,030 --> 00:32:40,360
Actually, I've decided

652
00:32:40,950 --> 00:32:42,230
to leave Qionghua.

653
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:45,270
I'm here to see you for the last time.

654
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:49,110
I don't like Qionghua.

655
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:51,240
Mengli wants to leave too.

656
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,570
I made a deal with Lingsha.

657
00:32:54,050 --> 00:32:56,770
We will never be apart no matter where we go.

658
00:32:58,390 --> 00:32:59,110
Tianhe,

659
00:33:02,410 --> 00:33:04,770
even if I want you to stay,

660
00:33:08,330 --> 00:33:09,700
you wouldn't want to?

661
00:33:10,490 --> 00:33:11,240
Maybe

662
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:13,890
I really don't belong here.

663
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:17,930
I returned the Kun Scale to you

664
00:33:18,850 --> 00:33:20,180
to fulfill my parents

665
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:21,480
and my wish.

666
00:33:23,020 --> 00:33:23,620
Brother,

667
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:26,530
if war breaks out with the Huanming Realm,

668
00:33:26,530 --> 00:33:27,480
promise me

669
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:29,400
to protect yourself.

670
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:35,300
In that case,

671
00:33:38,060 --> 00:33:39,680
you've made up your mind.

672
00:33:41,730 --> 00:33:43,790
Everyone has their own aspirations.

673
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:47,240
How can I possibly force you to stay?

674
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:50,060
Then, I'll be on my way.

675
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:56,470
Brother.

676
00:34:07,650 --> 00:34:08,330
Thank you.

677
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,790
Jing Chen said

678
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:45,010
the war 19 years ago

679
00:34:45,530 --> 00:34:48,639
started because Qionghua killed the innocent for its own gains.

680
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,969
Huanming was innocent.

681
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,440
What exactly does that mean?

682
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:54,170
Are you questioning me on behalf of those humans?

683
00:34:57,890 --> 00:34:58,480
Guixie.

684
00:34:59,020 --> 00:35:00,670
I'm the young master of the Huanming Realm.

685
00:35:00,670 --> 00:35:02,840
It's only natural for me to want to know the past.

686
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,480
Answer my questions.

687
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:06,150
Tell me the truth.

688
00:35:06,430 --> 00:35:08,030
So what if you know the truth?

689
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:10,330
Will you kill those humans?

690
00:35:10,350 --> 00:35:10,990
Brother.

691
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,890
Don't be rude to Young Master.

692
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,670
Every 19 years in the Huanming Realm,

693
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:22,080
the Heavenly Trail will move to the peak of Kunxu.

694
00:35:22,080 --> 00:35:22,960
19 years ago,

695
00:35:23,350 --> 00:35:25,400
Qionghua suddenly attacked the Huanming Realm

696
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:27,260
and brought disaster to our clan.

697
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:29,800
In that battle, tens of thousands of demon soldiers of our clan died.

698
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:31,710
Out of the 6 guardians, my brother and I were the only 2 left.

699
00:35:31,710 --> 00:35:33,300
Lord Chan You had to leave

700
00:35:33,330 --> 00:35:35,440
you, who was just born, to fight in the Mortal Realm.

701
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:37,440
She was hurt by Qionghua's Tai Qing,

702
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,980
and her health is getting worse each day.

703
00:35:38,980 --> 00:35:40,910
She can't fight Qionghua anymore.

704
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,580
Now, only you can protect

705
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:47,210
the numerous citizens of Huanming Realm from being slaughtered by Qionghua.

706
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:48,730
Young Master.

707
00:35:49,350 --> 00:35:50,470
For your mother,

708
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:52,370
and the lives of our clansmen,

709
00:35:53,270 --> 00:35:54,670
please come back with us.

710
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,800
Let me think about it for a night.

711
00:36:00,100 --> 00:36:02,020
I want to wait for Tianhe and Lingsha to come back.

712
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:02,730
Come back?

713
00:36:03,540 --> 00:36:05,400
Yun Tianhe is the host of Wangshu.

714
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:08,080
Qionghua would rather kill him than let him go.

715
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:08,590
Why?

716
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:11,500
You're a disciple of the Qionghua Sect, but you didn't know?

717
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:12,970
Qionghua must rely on a host

718
00:36:12,970 --> 00:36:15,000
to control Xihe and Wangshu, combining them

719
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,600
to open Huanming's barrier.

720
00:36:17,140 --> 00:36:17,740
Tell me.

721
00:36:18,450 --> 00:36:21,100
How could Qionghua Sect let Yun Tianhe go?

722
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:22,600
Isn't Tianhe in danger?

723
00:36:23,170 --> 00:36:24,690
I have to go to Qionghua to find them.

724
00:36:24,690 --> 00:36:25,690
No, Young Master.

725
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:27,200
Xuan Xiao has all three cold weapons.

726
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,110
Once the ice breaks,

727
00:36:28,110 --> 00:36:28,950
with his spiritual cultivation,

728
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:30,700
he will recognize your identity.

729
00:36:30,700 --> 00:36:33,310
Tianhe, Lingsha, and I will live and die together.

730
00:36:33,310 --> 00:36:34,890
How can I ignore their lives?

731
00:36:34,890 --> 00:36:35,550
Step aside.

732
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:09,760
Ziying.

733
00:37:10,570 --> 00:37:11,300
I know

734
00:37:12,010 --> 00:37:13,670
you are very angry with me now.

735
00:37:13,910 --> 00:37:15,480
You must be very sad about

736
00:37:16,210 --> 00:37:17,840
Sister Shen's passing as well.

737
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:20,870
Master Su Shen died after meeting Guixie.

738
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,210
I will

739
00:37:23,390 --> 00:37:26,050
take revenge on the Dream Tapir Demons for this.

740
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,600
I can't explain much to you now.

741
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,430
But thank you.

742
00:37:36,140 --> 00:37:36,870
Would you...

743
00:37:37,410 --> 00:37:38,270
I waited for you

744
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:40,510
to get back the Wangshu Sword for us.

745
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:41,910
Leave the sword.

746
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:44,530
We have nothing to do with each other anymore.

747
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:53,790
I see.

748
00:37:56,140 --> 00:37:57,740
I'll return the sword to you.

749
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:00,790
My father said that material possessions

750
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:03,130
will never be more important than people.

751
00:38:03,130 --> 00:38:04,930
This sword belongs to Qionghua.

752
00:38:05,490 --> 00:38:06,750
Take it back to report.

753
00:38:17,690 --> 00:38:18,330
Ziying,

754
00:38:20,850 --> 00:38:22,130
this is the second time

755
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:25,960
you said you don't want to get involved with me anymore.

756
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:27,640
But it doesn't matter.

757
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:30,510
In my heart,

758
00:38:31,830 --> 00:38:33,360
you'll always be my family.

759
00:38:38,530 --> 00:38:40,790
When you insisted on protecting demons,

760
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:43,980
you were no longer my family,

761
00:38:46,310 --> 00:38:47,510
but my enemy.

762
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:23,550
Yun Tianhe.

763
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:24,710
I will never

764
00:39:24,730 --> 00:39:26,630
let a traitor like you leave the mountain.

765
00:39:26,630 --> 00:39:28,240
Grandmaster permitted us to leave the mountain.

766
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:28,770
What?

767
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:31,230
You dare to disobey Grandmaster's order?

768
00:39:34,030 --> 00:39:34,760
Junior Xu Yi.

769
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:37,120
Grandmaster has ordered them to leave.

770
00:39:37,270 --> 00:39:38,980
Senior, you want to help this traitor.

771
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:40,180
But I don't want that.

772
00:39:40,430 --> 00:39:40,990
Ziying,

773
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:43,490
they are no longer your disciples.

774
00:39:43,870 --> 00:39:45,530
Do you still want to help them?

775
00:39:46,040 --> 00:39:47,970
I only obey Grandmaster's orders.

776
00:39:49,960 --> 00:39:50,890
Let them go.

777
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:05,890
-Mengli?
-Mengli?

778
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:09,080
Why are you back?

779
00:40:09,250 --> 00:40:10,580
You're just a disciple.

780
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:12,590
You overestimate yourself.

781
00:40:19,370 --> 00:40:19,920
Mengli!

782
00:41:17,430 --> 00:41:19,590
I still couldn't stop her.

783
00:41:19,890 --> 00:41:21,890
She's actually a Dream Tapir Demon?

784
00:41:24,680 --> 00:41:26,250
Master Zong Lian was a good person.

785
00:41:26,250 --> 00:41:27,780
But he was killed by a demon.

786
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,600
I’m destined to be sworn enemies

787
00:41:29,810 --> 00:41:31,210
with Dream Tapir Demons.

788
00:41:34,640 --> 00:41:35,790
Mengli is a demon?

789
00:41:36,170 --> 00:41:37,010
Yun Tianhe.

790
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:38,320
you gave up Qionghua

791
00:41:38,510 --> 00:41:40,150
for a demon?

792
00:41:40,470 --> 00:41:41,350
Why?

793
00:41:41,610 --> 00:41:42,530
I'm sorry, Ziying.

794
00:41:42,530 --> 00:41:44,990
I just want to save as many lives as possible.

795
00:41:52,220 --> 00:41:52,900
Yun Tianhe.

796
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:55,570
Mengli is your reason, right?

797
00:42:04,260 --> 00:42:06,150
Mengli, your demon identity is exposed.

798
00:42:06,150 --> 00:42:07,350
They won't let you go.

799
00:42:07,790 --> 00:42:08,860
You and Lingsha go first.

800
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:09,720
I'll stop them.

801
00:42:10,060 --> 00:42:10,990
Let's go together.

802
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:11,630
Demon!

803
00:42:11,990 --> 00:42:13,820
You actually hid in our sect.

804
00:42:14,110 --> 00:42:16,110
I'll kill you here today.

805
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:17,730
Prepare the formation!

806
00:42:31,090 --> 00:42:31,850
Get lost!

807
00:42:32,330 --> 00:42:33,760
My patience is limited.

808
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,610
Young Master, let's go.

809
00:42:54,710 --> 00:42:55,350
Go!

810
00:43:10,230 --> 00:43:11,960
Qionghua is not a place

811
00:43:11,990 --> 00:43:13,750
where demons like you can come and go as you like.

812
00:43:13,750 --> 00:43:14,310
Go.

813
00:43:14,820 --> 00:43:15,350
Let's go.

814
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:16,690
Stop them!

815
00:43:32,680 --> 00:43:33,380
Uncle.

816
00:43:37,850 --> 00:43:39,220
What's wrong, Qingyang?

817
00:43:39,220 --> 00:43:41,060
What a strong Dream Tapir Demon aura.
